      "date": "2012-10-12 08:10:36.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/245b15dc-1441-11e2-8ca0-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
